OL,3,CMet Office explains why amber weather
OL,4,Cwarning wasn't issued for Storm Bert
OL,6,FThe Met Office has explained why only
OL,7,Fa yellow weather warning was issued
OL,8,Fahead of Storm Bert amid questions
OL,9,Fabout whether a more severe warning
OL,10,Fshould have been in place.
OL,12,FA yellow warning was in place prior to
OL,13,Fthe heavy rainfall during Storm Bert
OL,14,Fat the weekend, which left many
OL,15,Fcommunities in south Wales flooded for
OL,16,Fthe second time in less than five
OL,17,Fyears.
OL,19,FQuestions have been asked by Rhondda
OL,20,FCynon Taf leaders and residents about
OL,21,Fwhy an amber warning was not issued.
