OL,3,CMet Office explains why amber weather
OL,4,Cwarning wasn't issued for Storm Bert
OL,6,FWill Lang, head of risk and resilient
OL,7,Fservices at the Met Office, said: "(It
OL,8,Fwas) a weekend of nasty weather for
OL,9,FWales and the whole of the UK and our
OL,10,Fthoughts very much go out to those
OL,11,Faffected by storm Bert in recent days.
OL,13,F"We saw there was the inklings of a
OL,14,Fstorm in the Atlantic as early as last
OL,15,Fweek. We issued our first yellow
OL,16,Fweather warnings as on Wednesday.
