OL,3,CMet Office explains why amber weather
OL,4,Cwarning wasn't issued for Storm Bert
OL,6,F"Those were rainfall warnings that
OL,7,Falready started to talk about
OL,8,Fsignificant flooding risk to homes,
OL,9,Fbusinesses and communities and a
OL,10,Fdanger to life, even, from flood water
OL,11,Fand around 150mm of rain.
OL,13,F"We then refined that warning in the
OL,14,Ffollowing days and we had the
OL,15,Fsignificant rainfall over Saturday
OL,16,Fnight which led to the flooding on
OL,17,FSunday morning.
