OL,3,CMet Office explains why amber weather
OL,4,Cwarning wasn't issued for Storm Bert
OL,6,FQuestions have been asked by those
OL,7,Faffected by the flooding this weekend
OL,8,Fand in 2020. In the run-up to Storm
OL,9,FDennis, an amber weather warning was
OL,10,Fput in place.
OL,12,FMr Lang said the circumstances for
OL,13,FStorm Bert were different to the ones
OL,14,Fleading up to Storm Dennis.
