OL,3,CMet Office explains why amber weather
OL,4,Cwarning wasn't issued for Storm Bert
OL,6,FHe said: "There are some similarities
OL,7,Fwith Storm Dennis. One difference is
OL,8,Fthat we didn't have the immediate wet
OL,9,Fweather like before Storm Dennis,
OL,10,Fobviously in the form of Storm Ciara
OL,11,Fjust a few days before (in 2020),
OL,12,Fwhich made things even more sensitive
OL,13,Fand even more flood risk.
