OL,3,CMet Office explains why amber weather
OL,4,Cwarning wasn't issued for Storm Bert
OL,6,F"It wasn't as clear cut, from our
OL,7,Fflood models and our weather models,
OL,8,Fthat the flood risk was as great at
OL,9,Fthe time. Although there was some
OL,10,Flocally significant impacts,
OL,11,Fparticularly in the South Wales
OL,12,FValleys as we headed into Sunday
OL,13,Fmorning."
