OL,3,CMet Office explains why amber weather
OL,4,Cwarning wasn't issued for Storm Bert
OL,6,FRhondda Cynon Taf County Borough
OL,7,FCouncil, South Wales Fire and Rescue,
OL,8,FNatural Resources Wales (NRW) and
OL,9,FSouth Wales Police declared a major
OL,10,Fincident for Rhondda Cynon Taf on
OL,11,FSunday, 24 November, with record river
OL,12,Flevels recorded on the River Taff on
OL,13,FSaturday night.
OL,15,FOne business owner in Pontypridd told
OL,16,FITV Wales: "We're the only business on
OL,17,Fthe street. Water just burst through
OL,18,Fthe doors. It was incredible. We had
OL,19,Fto climb the walls to get in.
