OL,3,CMet Office explains why amber weather
OL,4,Cwarning wasn't issued for Storm Bert
OL,6,F"We've had about #6,000 worth of
OL,7,Fdamage and stripped out all of the
OL,8,Fcarpets as well as helping the
OL,9,Fneighbours. It was a crazy day.
OL,11,F"It needs a big re-think because this
OL,12,Fis the first storm of the season as
OL,13,Fwell. This could be happening again
OL,14,Fthis winter so the authorities really
OL,15,Fneed to think this through."
OL,17,FMr Lang says he understands the
OL,18,Ffrustration from people affected by
OL,19,Fthe floods and ensured lessons will be
OL,20,Flearned as we enter storm season.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/13
