OL,3,CMet Office explains why amber weather
OL,4,Cwarning wasn't issued for Storm Bert
OL,6,FHe said: "There are always strong
OL,7,Fopinions, always emotive responses,
OL,8,Falways feedback to be taken in and
OL,9,Flessons learned.
OL,11,F"We are listening and we are
OL,12,Fconducting a thorough review with our
OL,13,Fpartners. After every significant
OL,14,Fweather event, including a named
OL,15,Fstorm, we review how the weather
OL,16,Fwarnings went out.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
