OL,3,CMet Office explains why amber weather
OL,4,Cwarning wasn't issued for Storm Bert
OL,6,F"With this one we will be reaching out
OL,7,Fto our partners and working out how
OL,8,Fthe (weather) warnings but also the
OL,9,Fflood warnings went as well and
OL,10,Fcommunication between the
OL,11,Forganisations and how the message got
OL,12,Fout to the vulnerable communities.
OL,14,F"Those findings will be coming out in
OL,15,Fdue course. We are keen to learn what
OL,16,Fwent well and what didn't go well and
OL,17,Fimplement it as soon as possible.
