OL,3,CMet Office explains why amber weather
OL,4,Cwarning wasn't issued for Storm Bert
OL,6,F"We are at the start of flood season.
OL,7,FI'm not saying there will be further
OL,8,Fflooding in south Wales, but we need
OL,9,Fto be mindful we're at that time of
OL,10,Fyear and we need to be prepared."
OL,12,FImmediate financial support will be
OL,13,Fprovided to people whose homes have
OL,14,Fbeen flooded during Storm Bert.
OL,16,FThe Welsh Government will fund local
OL,17,Fauthorities to provide grants of
OL,18,F#1,000 for households without
OL,19,Finsurance cover, or #500 to affected
OL,20,Fhouseholds with existing insurance
OL,21,Fcover.
